 class="t m166 xf h1d y3d9 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How has this lesson changed your view of temperance? </div><div class="t m400 x8d h1d y512 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m3d3 xf h1d y64b ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">After studying this week&apos;s lesson, how would you explain </div><div class="t m8a xf h1d y64c ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Christian concept of self-control to a curious neighbor? </div><div class="t m3f7 x4d h1d y64d ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUMMARY: True temperance is refusing to use or do any-</div><div class="t m568 x4d h1d y514 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thing harmful and using or doing in moderation those things </div><div class="t m35f x4d h1d y4a6 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">which are good. It is motivated by our love for God and fellow </div><div class="t m5fe x4d h1d y3e1 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">human beings. And we receive the strength for it from our </div><div class="t m32e x4d h1d y4a7 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">heavenly Father. </div><div class="t m1ea x2b h1d y64e ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Did you give a Thirteenth Sabbath Offering second </div><div class="t m27a x31 h1d yf8 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">quarter of 1987? </div><div class="t m431 x2b h1d y64f ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">If so, you helped to build this girls&apos; dormitory at Nile </div><div class="t m185 x31 h1d yfa ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Union Academy in Egypt. </div><div class="t m5ff x2b h1d yfb ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The attached fields, not part of an organized divi-</div><div class="t m566 x31 h1d y650 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sion, are union territories directed from the General </div><div class="t m443 x31 h1d y651 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Conference headquarters. </div><div class="t m600 x2b h1d y652 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Help them again this Thirteenth Sabbath. </div><div class="t m601 x71 h1d y652 ff5 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">See back </div><div class="t m4f7 x31 h1d y653 ff5 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cover </div><div class="t m54b x59 h1